00:49.258 --> 00:51.092
Go on, Barbara.

00:53.637 --> 00:56.681
We go back to our homeroom
for dismissal.

00:56.849 --> 00:59.851
Unless you have a pass
for sports or something.

01:02.563 --> 01:04.688
Is that what you did
on the day in question?

01:05.357 --> 01:08.818
No. Mr. Gettys asked me
to stay after class.

01:09.027 --> 01:10.903
What happened next, Barbara?

01:11.071 --> 01:13.740
He told me to sit
in the chair beside his desk.

01:13.907 --> 01:15.199
Barbara.

01:15.367 --> 01:18.661
If you will, in your own words,
tell us exactly what happened...

01:18.871 --> 01:20.872
in the next few minutes.

01:21.290 --> 01:23.875
I told him I was afraid I'd miss my bus.

01:24.042 --> 01:27.879
He promised I'd get to the bus on time
if I'd help him do something.

01:28.046 --> 01:33.050
Then, before I could say anything,
he placed his hand inside my blouse.

01:34.470 --> 01:38.014
I was so frightened. I didn't move.
I thought if I was just quiet it'd be okay.

01:38.223 --> 01:42.101
Then his other hand went up
under inside my skirt.

01:43.020 --> 01:45.062
Then, with his hand...

01:45.230 --> 01:47.857
he started moving back and forth...

01:48.025 --> 01:50.818
farther and farther inside my skirt.

01:51.028 --> 01:54.363
He said he was testing to see
if I had any special feelings...

01:54.573 --> 01:57.658
that he wanted to see
what kind of feelings I had.

01:57.826 --> 02:00.870
I was trying to think of something to say,
but I couldn't.

02:01.038 --> 02:02.789
I was confused, and he just kept on.

02:02.956 --> 02:06.000
I asked him to stop,
but it was like he couldn't hear.

02:06.168 --> 02:08.669
He just kept on with his hand.

02:08.836 --> 02:10.505
Then I screamed.

02:10.672 --> 02:14.133
Then he got mad and said
we'd have to try it again sometime.

02:14.551 --> 02:16.552
Did he try again?

02:16.720 --> 02:18.346
Not with me.

02:18.514 --> 02:20.139
But with your friends?

02:20.307 --> 02:21.808
Yes.

02:22.559 --> 02:26.479
And after you had told them
what he had done to you...

02:27.648 --> 02:32.276
they told you
what he had done to them!

02:33.153 --> 02:34.362
Isn't that true?

02:34.530 --> 02:36.239
Yes.

02:39.368 --> 02:41.285
I have nothing further.

02:43.247 --> 02:46.415
Your witness, Mr. Lomax.

02:53.549 --> 02:55.550
Any chance, Your Honor,
for a short recess?

02:55.717 --> 02:57.009
Of course.

02:57.177 --> 02:59.887
This court will be in recess
for 15 minutes.

03:03.934 --> 03:06.477
- Honey, what...?
- Not now, Bernice.

03:11.692 --> 03:13.901
Lomax, what's wrong?

03:14.069 --> 03:16.863
As your attorney, I'm advising you
to keep the fuck away from me.

03:17.030 --> 03:18.990
Why? What are you talking about?

03:19.157 --> 03:22.618
The wife, the kid, the outrage.
You definitely had me fooled.

03:22.786 --> 03:25.037
Hey, you're my lawyer.

03:25.372 --> 03:26.539
You're here to defend me.

03:26.707 --> 03:30.418
Know what I think? Why not put you on
the stand? You can jerk off for the judge.

03:30.586 --> 03:33.462
- You know she's lying.
- Get the hell away from me.

03:54.818 --> 03:56.903
Well, hell, there you are.

03:58.071 --> 04:00.531
Rumor was you were out
wandering in traffic.

04:01.241 --> 04:02.700
Not now, Larry.

04:02.868 --> 04:07.455
What's the game plan?
I got a 4:30 deadline. I need a quote.

04:07.623 --> 04:08.831
Give me a quote.

04:08.999 --> 04:10.041
Fuck off.

04:12.753 --> 04:16.797
Mr. Lomax had no comment
on today's events.

04:16.964 --> 04:19.716
Speculation, however, was widespread...

04:19.885 --> 04:23.888
that the young lawyer's
unblemished string of victories...

04:24.056 --> 04:25.598
would come to an end...

04:25.766 --> 04:27.975
in this courtroom.

04:33.106 --> 04:34.815
It was a nice run, Kev.

04:34.983 --> 04:37.193
Had to close out someday.

04:37.694 --> 04:39.570
Nobody wins them all.

05:01.385 --> 05:03.219
Have you had any discipline problems...

05:03.387 --> 05:05.262
in math class this year?

05:05.430 --> 05:06.889
No.

05:07.766 --> 05:09.225
No?

05:09.810 --> 05:13.521
Hasn't Mr. Gettys had to talk to you
repeatedly about your behavior?

05:13.689 --> 05:16.148
Isn't that why he asked you
to stay after class?

05:16.316 --> 05:17.650
No.

05:20.070 --> 05:22.613
Have other teachers asked you
to stay after class?

05:22.781 --> 05:24.073
Once or twice.

05:24.241 --> 05:28.077
- Did they want to talk about your behavior?
- Objection. Immaterial.

05:28.245 --> 05:30.621
- Goes to motive.
- Overruled.

05:30.789 --> 05:32.623
You may answer the question.

05:32.791 --> 05:34.792
I don't know
what the other teachers wanted.

05:34.960 --> 05:36.877
You'd have to talk to them.

05:39.089 --> 05:42.425
You ever pass notes in class, Barbara?

05:44.011 --> 05:45.720
Maybe a note that...

05:45.887 --> 05:47.263
made fun of Mr. Gettys?

05:47.431 --> 05:49.682
- No.
- No?

05:49.850 --> 05:53.436
Never called him
a disgusting pig monster?

05:55.355 --> 05:56.647
Order.

05:58.150 --> 05:59.608
No.

05:59.776 --> 06:02.278
Your Honor, I've pre-marked this
Defense Exhibit A.

06:02.446 --> 06:06.115
Objection. We've had plenty of time
for discovery here.

06:06.283 --> 06:08.951
I'm going to let this in, Mr. Lomax.

06:09.119 --> 06:12.496
I'm also going to suggest
that if you have any other exhibits...

06:12.664 --> 06:15.791
you present them in a timely fashion,
or not at all.

06:17.961 --> 06:20.880
I'm sorry, Barbara, I was wrong.

06:21.048 --> 06:23.382
It's huge hog beast.

06:24.760 --> 06:26.469
This is your handwriting, isn't it?

06:26.636 --> 06:28.763
- Yes, but...
- You wrote this in Gettys' class.

06:28.930 --> 06:32.058
- It's a joke.
- "He's a huge hog beast."

06:32.225 --> 06:35.728
He probably eats
a thousand pancakes for breakfast."

06:38.065 --> 06:40.066
You're writing about Mr. Gettys,
aren't you?

06:40.233 --> 06:43.194
It was meant to be a joke.

06:44.780 --> 06:47.698
Have you ever had a party
at your house, Barbara...

06:47.866 --> 06:49.408
when your parents were away?

06:49.576 --> 06:51.744
Objection. Your Honor,
this is way out of line.

06:51.912 --> 06:54.371
- Credibility and bias.
- Overruled.

06:54.539 --> 06:56.665
Answer the question.

06:57.459 --> 06:59.043
Yes.

07:00.337 --> 07:04.048
Have you ever heard of a game
called "Special Places"?

07:05.801 --> 07:08.010
You're under oath, Barbara.

07:08.178 --> 07:10.096
A man's career...

07:10.263 --> 07:11.680
his reputation...

07:11.848 --> 07:15.392
his life is on the line.
This is not a joke.

07:15.560 --> 07:19.480
Have you ever played
the game "Special Places"?

07:24.277 --> 07:25.569
Yes.

07:25.737 --> 07:28.614
Is this game sexual in nature?

07:30.200 --> 07:33.619
Is this game sexual in nature?

07:33.787 --> 07:36.497
We only played it once.

07:36.665 --> 07:39.208
This special party, Barbara...

07:39.376 --> 07:44.338
this was the first time you told the
story about Mr. Gettys, wasn't it?

07:44.506 --> 07:45.673
Yes.

07:45.841 --> 07:49.260
I've spoken to other children
who were there that day.

07:49.427 --> 07:52.429
Is there anything else
they may have told me about the party?

07:52.597 --> 07:56.058
Objection. If he has other witnesses,
let him call them.

07:56.226 --> 07:58.060
If I need to call
those other children, I will.

07:58.228 --> 08:01.063
I'm going to sustain that, Mr. Lomax.

08:01.231 --> 08:03.399
Rephrase your question.

08:08.196 --> 08:10.489
You threatened those children,
didn't you?

08:10.699 --> 08:12.158
That's not the way it happened.

08:12.325 --> 08:16.495
You told them to lie, to falsely claim
that Mr. Gettys had hurt them.

08:16.705 --> 08:18.205
These things did happen.

08:18.415 --> 08:23.210
If they didn't, you were going
to tell everyone about this special party.

08:23.378 --> 08:24.837
They happened to me.

08:25.005 --> 08:27.923
So you made up a story. A special story.

08:28.091 --> 08:29.633
A story about a math teacher...

08:29.801 --> 08:32.219
who was tough on you,
who kept you after class.

08:32.386 --> 08:35.054
A huge hog beast you didn't like!

08:35.222 --> 08:37.099
That's what really happened, isn't it?

08:37.308 --> 08:38.517
No.

08:38.727 --> 08:41.729
I didn't want to be the only one.

08:43.315 --> 08:45.691
You goddamn lowlife, son of a bitch...

08:45.901 --> 08:48.068
You leave that girl alone,
that's enough.

08:49.613 --> 08:51.363
Bailiff, evict that man.

08:51.531 --> 08:53.240
No further questions, Your Honor.

08:53.450 --> 08:55.659
I'm going to adjourn for the day.

08:55.827 --> 08:59.997
We'll be back here at 9:00 in the morning
and people will behave themselves...

09:00.207 --> 09:01.665
You made me proud.

09:01.875 --> 09:03.918
Or find themselves in contempt.

09:04.127 --> 09:05.169
Good evening.

09:08.882 --> 09:12.968
Pack it up, baby. You need a drink.

09:14.888 --> 09:17.514
- You go, Gators.
- Yeah.

09:17.682 --> 09:22.353
