09:34.741 --> 09:35.991
Larry.

09:36.159 --> 09:39.119
Why don't you quit being a party pooper?
Have yourself a drink.

09:39.329 --> 09:41.830
We're not going to discuss
the damn case anymore.

09:42.040 --> 09:43.165
Am I right?

09:43.333 --> 09:44.917
I'll drink to that.

09:46.628 --> 09:49.004
No shop talk.

09:52.926 --> 09:54.260
- Pour me another.
- Hey, baby.

09:54.427 --> 09:56.011
Lomax, you're wild.

09:56.179 --> 09:58.597
I feel one of them nights coming on.

10:01.685 --> 10:03.102
I've seen the Eiffel Tower

10:03.270 --> 10:04.937
And I've seen the Taj Mahal

10:05.105 --> 10:08.649
