11:00.660 --> 11:02.703
I've had some sympathetic juries.

11:02.912 --> 11:05.164
That's exactly what we're looking for.

11:05.373 --> 11:08.417
We want you to come to New York,
help us pick a jury.

11:13.840 --> 11:15.299
I tell you, man...

11:15.467 --> 11:18.052
you're pretty damn good.

11:18.553 --> 11:20.054
Your card is great.

11:20.221 --> 11:22.556
And the black thing, you being black...

11:22.724 --> 11:24.641
Whose idea was that? Paul's?

11:24.809 --> 11:26.143
That's just brilliant.

11:26.353 --> 11:29.021
I'm just not drunk enough yet
to fall for it.

11:29.356 --> 11:30.856
I'll buy you a drink when I...

11:31.066 --> 11:33.192
