12:58.987 --> 13:02.906
Why do I feel the hand of Mary Ann
on this adventure?

13:04.492 --> 13:07.786
I gotta tell you, Ma,
this routine's getting awful tired.

13:08.079 --> 13:09.746
Working on Sunday.

13:09.998 --> 13:12.499
Working? Ma, get over it.

13:13.877 --> 13:16.670
Ma. Listen to me. I love my wife.

13:17.088 --> 13:20.007
Okay? I love her all the way.

13:20.175 --> 13:21.508
