Just this room.

50:08.673 --> 50:10.924
And a bedroom?

50:11.092 --> 50:13.802
Nope. No bedroom.

50:13.969 --> 50:16.471
- Where does he sleep?
- Who says he sleeps?

50:16.639 --> 50:17.722
Where does he fuck?

50:17.890 --> 50:19.849
