01:10:11.916 --> 01:10:13.834
Unbelievable.

01:10:14.210 --> 01:10:15.502
Wide is the gate...

01:10:15.670 --> 01:10:18.797
and broad is the way
that leadeth to temptation.

01:10:18.965 --> 01:10:20.674
